<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>SQL Injection - Vulnerable Lab</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-container">
    <div class="py-4">
      <h1 class="mb-2">SQL Injection</h1>
      <p class="text-muted">This page demonstrates a classic SQL injection vulnerability in a search endpoint. The demo query uses unescaped user input directly in SQL.</p>

      <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5>SQL Injection Demo Pages</h5>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Login SQLi:</strong> Bypass authentication with SQL injection</li>
            <li><strong>Registration SQLi:</strong> Inject SQL during signup</li>
            <li><strong>Search SQLi:</strong> Extract data through search queries</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="d-flex gap-2">
            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary">Login SQLi</a>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Registration SQLi</a>
            <a href="/search" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Search SQLi</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5>Payloads to Try</h5>
          <ul>
            <li><code>admin' OR '1'='1</code> - Basic bypass</li>
            <li><code>' OR 1=1 -- -</code> - Comment injection</li>
            <li><code>' UNION SELECT null,null --</code> - Union injection</li>
            <li><code>'; DROP TABLE users--</code> - Destructive (careful!)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="btn btn-link">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>